{
  "stem": "11998.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And especially, when we still lived in the town, Polish groups would come in-- kids would come in, and they would attack women in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would rob people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we became sort of a group of vigilantes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we started to roam the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when we caught somebody, we would beat them up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that, of course, sent the message out that it's not-- it's not-- it's no, not such easy pickings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] You know, it's an interesting situation, that I don't even remember the name of my very close friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's something that-- as if it got wiped out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were boys that were mostly older than myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- let's see, I was 14, and some of them were 15, 16, 17.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- they was quite strong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- you know, I mean, one-- one occasion, I caught-- I stopped a-- a rock with my glasses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, it was a terrible situation, because, to replace your glasses in the ghetto was very expensive and very difficult.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they broke my glass, and I was lucky that none of the glass got into my eye.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I saved my eye this way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But so, life went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you were always hoping that-- I mean, I was-- I worked as an electrician.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after hours, I went to people's homes, and they wanted to add a plug, or another light.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was working for this family, the German family, Jewish-German family, who was deported from Germany into Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they had a crippled-- I mean, a disabled child that was in a wheelchair.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She must have been about 20 or 30 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe she was more than 20.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was about 30 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
